name: Elephant Mountain 🐘🗻 - 象山

location.address: Luodong Night Market (Zhongshan Park), Luodong Township, Yilan County, Taiwan

name: Nightmarket 🌃- 羅東夜市
description:
The best night market in the east side of Taiwan ! You will be able to try out plenty of typical food (stinky tofu, pig blood...). 
However, it is very crowded.

location.address: Penghu, Magong City, Penghu County, Taiwan

name: Penghu Island 🏝- 彭湖
description:
A hidden gem that feels like paradise !
It's an island located in the West side of Taiwan, you can go there by plane easily.

location.address: No. 279, Gongzheng Road, Luodong Township, Yilan County, Taiwan 265

name: Ban Fang Dumplings 🥢🥟- 八方雲集
description: A very good street food spot if you like fried dumplings ! The staff is very nice.

location.address: Taiwan, Nantou County, Xinyi Township, 玉山

name: YuShan 🧗🏻‍♀️🏔 - 玉山
description:
The highest peak of south-east Asia !
If you are in a good shape and love new adventure, this is for you.

name: Sanqing Temple ☯️ - 三清宮
description: Ornate Taoist place of worship featuring traditional Taiwanese architecture & sweeping mountain views.

location.address: Taiwan, New Taipei City, Ruifang District, 九份

name: Jiufen 🏯- 九份
description: A incredible town full of surprises and easily accessible from Taipei (by bus).

location.address: Ximen, Zhongzheng District, Taipei City, Taiwan

name: Ximen 🏙- 西門
description: Located in the heart of Taipei City, this is very cool spot for young people with a lot of shops and restaurant.
